translation.lt: Atlikus Chi-kvadrato testą rasta statistiškai reikšminga asociacija tarp {x_name} ir {y_name} ({chi_rs}).
translation.en: Pearson's Chi-square test showed a statistically significant association between {x_name} and {y_name} ({chi_rs}).

translation.lt: Atlikus Chi-kvadrato testą statistiškai reikšminga asociacija tarp {x_name} ir {y_name} nebuvo nustatyta ({chi_rs}).
translation.en: Pearson's Chi-square test did not show an association between {x_name} and {y_name} ({chi_rs}).
